<h1>Recurring Booking Created</h1>
<p>Dear <%= @user.full_name || @user.username %>,</p>
<p>Your recurring booking has been created with a total of <strong><%= @count %></strong> instances.</p>

<h3>Booking Summary</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Title:</strong> <%= @bookings.first.title %></li>
  <li><strong>Venue:</strong> <%= @venue_name %></li>
  <li><strong>Pattern:</strong> <%= @bookings.first.recurrence_pattern&.capitalize %></li>
  <li><strong>First Start:</strong> <%= @bookings.first.start_time.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M") %></li>
</ul>

<p>All bookings are currently <strong>pending confirmation</strong>.</p>
